Do follow the Steps To Get Customised Carousel - :)
	1- We need to install the dependency or library of owl-carousel in our project and for that library we need jquery and owl-carousel. 
		Step 1.1 - Install Script loader if you dont have
		run this command in your Cmd window on a specified path.
			"npm install script-loader"

		Step 1.2 - To install this owl-carousel library.
			"npm install ngx-owl-carousel --save"
		
		Step 1.3 - Specified import in your app.module.ts
			"import { OwlModule } from 'ngx-owl-carousel';"

		Step 1.4 - Do Specify the module in imports array
			"OwlModule",

		Step 1.5 - Open angular.json file and Specify the path in style array and js array
			""styles": [
				    "./node_modules/owl.carousel/dist/assets/owl.carousel.css",
				    "./node_modules/owl.carousel/dist/assets/owl.theme.default.css"
					]"

			 "scripts": [
	              "./node_modules/jquery/dist/jquery.slim.min.js",
	              "./node_modules/bootstrap/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js",
	              "./node_modules/jquery/dist/jquery.js",
	              "./node_modules/owl.carousel/dist/owl.carousel.js",
	            	]	

		Step 1.6 - 	Copy the code as defined by file name
			
